			<h1>Greening Corporate Responsibility</h1>
			<br />
			<p>You are committed to environmental sustainability and reducing your organization's carbon footprint. You've improved your operations to make your organization run as environmentally efficiently as possible but have you considered what's happening beyond your office walls?
			<br /><br />Your employees are a huge asset in your quest to effect positive change. While encouraging employees to practice environmentally sound habits while at work is an excellent start, you can decrease their carbon footprint even further by encouraging them to use environmentally friendly products and services outside of the office - services like Kinek.
			<br /><br />When an employee reduces their carbon footprint as a result of information you have given them,<br />you are taking another step towards improving your own positive impact on the environment.</p>
			
			<hr />	
			
